{"tid":988883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Kpop] 一人一首叫雞沉船時聽既歌","createTime":"2019-01-20T12:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T14:01:51.000Z","uid":119290,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cada7c75ea291e98abb56b344f44adce370bd09f","tid":988883,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2O6dRaBbFoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2O6dRaBbFoo&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=70779b8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2O6dRaBbFoo</a><br />\n<br />\nBI: <br />\n<br />\n지나간 기억 속에서 산다는 건<br />\n活在過去的記憶裡<br />\n그 얼마나 무기력한 외로움일까<br />\n那會是多麼無力的孤獨啊<br />\n그 기억 속에서조차 잊혀진다는 건<br />\n連那些記憶裡的都遺忘了<br />\n또 어떤 순간보다 잔인한 아픔인가<br />\n又是比起任何瞬間 還要更加殘忍的痛苦<br />\n죽도록 사랑했건만 끝내 나 죽지 않았네<br />\n雖然曾愛的死去活來 結束了我也沒事呢<br />\n숨을 깊게 들이마셔도 내뱉으면 한숨이 돼<br />\n即使深吸一口氣 吐出來的話 還是變嘆息<br />\n누구나 하는 이별이니 우리 슬퍼 말아요<br />\n無論是誰都會面臨的離別 我們就不要悲傷了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">난 또 그대 닮은 듯 아닌 사람 찾아갈게요<br />\n我會再去尋找著和你不像的人</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句幾寫實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b9494d41f6811684bf67f14eb17220b85f5420","tid":988883,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6DyOU81eSSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6DyOU81eSSA&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1bf82d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6DyOU81eSSA</a>"},{"pid":"b8246a27eb6fff27dafea0e33bb190ac2b173eae","tid":988883,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"TT"},{"pid":"966b5c2bc7c34ace5dabefce857382aa44e6f06c","tid":988883,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"沉左船 第一時間重唔係諗WHAT IS LOVE?"},{"pid":"827